{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FTmytEe3CjLP8jGCT2QgHr","type":"tool_result","content":"# Harness Cost Report\n\nTotal API-equivalent cost: $334.36\nTotal API calls: 2543\nAverage cost per story: $3.45 (82 stories)\n\n## Cost by Token Type\n\n| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n|------|--------|------|------|---|\n| Cache reads | 137,373,484 | $1.50/MTok | $206.06 | 62% |\n| Cache writes | 3,950,160 | $18.75/MTok | $74.07 | 22% |\n| Output | 721,269 | $75/MTok | $54.10 | 16% |\n| Input | 8,965 | $15/MTok | $0.13 | 0% |\n\n## Cost by Phase\n\n| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| verify | 1230 | $150.81 | 45.1% |\n| orchestrator | 274 | $59.51 | 17.8% |\n| create-story | 315 | $36.14 | 10.8% |\n| dev-story | 300 | $33.68 | 10.1% |\n| code-review | 260 | $30.99 | 9.3% |\n| retro | 164 | $23.23 | 6.9% |\n\n## Cost by Tool\n\n| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n|------|-------|------|---|\n| Bash | 825 | $93.06 | 27.8% |\n| Read | 561 | $78.42 | 23.5% |\n| Edit | 490 | $61.22 | 18.3% |\n| Agent | 325 | $47.77 | 14.3% |\n| Skill | 58 | $20.96 | 6.3% |\n| Grep | 157 | $17.21 | 5.1% |\n| Write | 46 | $6.71 | 2.0% |\n| Glob | 51 | $5.32 | 1.6% |\n| TodoWrite | 26 | $3.35 | 1.0% |\n| ToolSearch | 4 | $0.33 | 0.1% |\n\n## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n\n| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| unknown | 197 | $51.19 | 15.3% |\n| 5-1-flow-execution-sequential-steps | 65 | $8.84 | 2.6% |\n| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 69 | $8.51 | 2.5% |\n| 17-1-worktree-manager | 57 | $8.24 | 2.5% |\n| 17-2-lane-pool | 61 | $7.58 | 2.3% |\n| 16-6-story-flow-execution | 53 | $7.15 | 2.1% |\n| 9-2-custom-workflow-creation | 64 | $6.83 | 2.0% |\n| 3-2-embedded-agent-templates | 49 | $6.42 | 1.9% |\n| 14-3-activity-display-driver-integration | 48 | $6.35 | 1.9% |\n| 16-3-telemetry-writer | 46 | $6.20 | 1.9% |\n[OK] Report saved to /Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01HD2FQ715hjYuGnBPGGv1RV","session_id":"be1634c4-ada6-4a14-ba2b-b0cd95b49a03","uuid":"0523df01-29e4-4b2e-a67b-095a450f9845","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:37:12.415Z"}
