usly.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a86a16d23e92154b9","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-04-04.md`.\n\n**Summary of findings:**\n\n- **Story 17-2-lane-pool** completed: all 12 ACs verified, committed as `66ec8b4`. Sprint is now at 49/64 stories done (76.6%), 0 failures.\n- **Session cost: $5.26** (36 API calls) — cheap because only verification + commit ran.\n- **Total sprint cost: $334.36** across 2,543 calls.\n- **Top issues:** (1) proof format mismatch required reformatting, (2) AGENTS.md not updated by dev-story subagent, (3) verification ran tests/coverage twice.\n- **Key action items:** Add AGENTS.md update to dev-story workflow, teach verification to use correct proof format by default, combine duplicate test runs in verification phase.\n- **Verification remains the #1 cost driver** at 45.1% of total spend ($150.81). The verification subagent's pattern of running tests twice (once to check, once to capture for proofs) is the most actionable optimization target."}],"totalDurationMs":80500,"totalTokens":28988,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2786,"cache_read_input_tokens":25907,"output_tokens":294,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2786},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
